{"tid":2141883,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大亨哥，要參選囉，咪淨係掛住隻抽","createTime":"2020-08-06T04:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:28:07.000Z","uid":38189,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"987d01c7603a1664a62b86418885f8fe6555dde6","tid":2141883,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"大亨哥，要參選囉，咪淨係掛住隻抽，<br />\n最弊落選左，無陰功咯，松泰亦愛莫能助。<br />\n<br />\n(落選左，無陰功咯，松泰亦愛莫能助)<br />\n<br />\n云根哥， 好高質喎，我日夜唱頌國師，<br />\n教導城邦囉，好波喎，令建制一肚火。<br />\n<br />\n(城邦歌，好波喎，令建制一肚火)<br />\n<br />\n四眼又要選議席，唔投佢確係無益，<br />\n泰博亦要多努力，延續那永續無敵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmojim.com&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=38423c75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mojim.com</a>，有好歌喎，詳盡字彙記錄更多，<br />\n如聽歌，找魔鏡，唔背熟就會捱餓。<br />\n<br />\n(如聽歌，找魔鏡，唔背熟就會捱餓)<br />\n<br />\n熱狗哥，一個個，我地日日記住隻歌，<br />\n人多多，RE ME RE DO 齊合力唱伴同和。<br />\n<br />\n(人多多，RE ME RE DO 齊合力唱伴同和)"},{"pid":"b14ede402d63245fb8200ed37eb27abffb14b09a","tid":2141883,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d43da45881dbe8a0dec73e412b4f5ae0f870d5","tid":2141883,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8048f8cde7c4158b26dccd45148fd221319c637","tid":2141883,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1325186ffffc48c0e4b8101a0c3d4c949570558c","tid":2141883,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p